---
title: Pea and Cannellini Bean Curry with tomato onion salsa and naan
description: This lightly spiced cannellini bean curry is already hearty, but is helped even more by the addition of a warm and fluffy naan. A tomato salsa adds a refreshing element to this delicious dish.
